text: Indiana Rose Evans is an Australian actress and singer. She was born in Sydney, Australia. She is known for portraying Matilda Hunter in Home and Away, Bella Hartley in H2O: Just Add Water and Emmaline Robinson in Blue Lagoon: The Awakening. ==Other websites== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:People from Sydney
